---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1>About Us</h1>
      <p>Two English-speaking parents on a Spanish-speaking mission</p>
    </header>

    <div class="content">
      <section class="card">
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>
          We're a family based in [your area] who decided to raise our kids speaking Spanishâ€”even though neither of us are native speakers. It started as an experiment and turned into a passion.
        </p>
        <p>
          We know firsthand how challenging (and rewarding!) it can be to create a bilingual environment when Spanish isn't your first language. That's why we started Learning in Dos: to share what we've learned and connect with other families on the same journey.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="card">
        <h2>What We Do</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Blog:</strong> We share our experiences, tips, and resources for raising bilingual kids as non-native speakers.</li>
          <li><strong>Play Groups:</strong> We organize Spanish-speaking play dates and activities in our community.</li>
          <li><strong>Community:</strong> We run a WhatsApp group where families can connect, share wins, ask questions, and support each other.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="card">
        <h2>Join Our Community</h2>
        <p>
          Want to connect with other families raising bilingual kids? Join our WhatsApp group! It's a supportive space for sharing resources, arranging play dates, and celebrating those small wins (like when your toddler finally says "agua" instead of "water").
        </p>
        <p>
          <em>Contact us to get the invite link!</em>
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 0;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .page-header p {
    color: var(--gray);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .content {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .card h2 {
    color: var(--blue);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .card p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .card p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .card ul {
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
  }

  .card li {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
</style>

